overview.en: FOB is committed to reshaping the competitive quiz industry structure through the blockchain, reshaping the production relationship, allowing value contributors to participate in industry value sharing, maximizing the productivity of each individual and realizing community building! Decentralization is the main goal and goal!
overview.zh: FOB致力于通过区块链重塑竞技竞猜行业结构，重塑生产关系，让价值贡献者参与行业价值分享，使每个个体的生产力得以最大释放，实现社区共建！以去中心化为主旨和目标！
